== 經貿關係 ==

越蒙贸易合作关系於1958年確立<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/越南与蒙古加强贸易交流合作/86715.amp | title=越南与蒙古加强贸易交流合作 | publisher=vietnamplus.vn | date=2018-10-06 | accessdate=2022-03-27 | archive-date=2020-11-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127075628/https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%8E%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C/86715.amp | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年，越南對蒙出口總額達570萬美元<ref name="trade">{{citation | url=http://vietnamplus.vn/kinhte-en/200812133227819315 | title=Vietnam, Mongolia aim for 10 million USD in trade | date=2008-12-13 | publisher=Vietnam News Agency| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007072520/http://www.vietnamplus.vn/kinhte-en/200812133227819315 | archivedate=2011-10-07 }}</ref>。蒙古主要从越南进口[[大米|大米]]、[[咖啡|咖啡]]、[[植物油|植物油]]、水产品等商品，越南則主要從蒙古進口[[煤炭|煤炭]]、冷冻肉制品、[[皮革|皮革]]等商品。<ref>{{Cite news | url= https://cn.dangcongsan.vn/news/越南促进与蒙古的经贸合作-544051.html | title= 越南促进与蒙古的经贸合作 | publisher= 越南共產黨電子報 | date= 2020-12-07 | accessdate= 2022-03-27 | archive-date= 2020-11-27 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201127133036/https://cn.dangcongsan.vn/news/%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%BF%83%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%8E%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E8%B4%B8%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-544051.html | dead-url= no }}</ref>


